+/*
+    RawSpeed - RAW file decoder.
+
+    Sony LLVC v3 ("Compressed HQ", ARW compression tag 32766) decompressor.
+
+    Reverse-engineered from the Adobe DNG Converter `sony_llvc3_dec` and ported
+    from a verified prototype. The codec is a line-based inverse-wavelet pipeline
+    related to Canon CRX (subband wavelet + adaptive entropy coding), but the
+    entropy coder, the flipped 5/3 lifting and the luma/chroma combine are
+    Sony-specific.
+
